      "writtenOn": "2026-06-10T16:33:39Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Critical] Line 127: `bodyOverwrite` from `pluginData` is used as the displayed message body without any validation or size limiting. Plugin-provided data can be less trusted than the original conversation body and may be rendered through the same rich text/link parsing path, so malformed or very large values could cause UI abuse or performance issues. Please validate this field before assigning it, using the same constraints expected for message bodies.\n\n```suggestion\nconst auto bodyOverwriteIt \u003d msg.pluginData.find(\"bodyOverwrite\");\nif (bodyOverwriteIt !\u003d msg.pluginData.end()\n    \u0026\u0026 !bodyOverwriteIt.value().isEmpty()\n    \u0026\u0026 bodyOverwriteIt.value().size() \u003c\u003d MAX_MESSAGE_BODY_SIZE) {\n    body \u003d bodyOverwriteIt.value();\n}\n```",
      "revId": "fa8277ee9bc89a7692ec2416b257b2ca8960291f",
      "serverId": "1e26b4c1-6b8c-47ff-9df7-501b633d3b5a"
    },
