      "side": 1,
      "message": "Line 136: Edition handling looks for `bodyOverwrite` inside each edition map, but the new type only adds `pluginData` at the top-level `SwarmMessage`. If the daemon stores plugin metadata only in `msg.pluginData`, edited-message history will not consistently show the plugin-overwritten body. Please confirm the daemon really injects `bodyOverwrite` into every edition entry; otherwise, carry edition plugin metadata explicitly or do not apply overwrite logic here.\n\n```suggestion\n// If editions need plugin-rendered bodies, expose edition plugin data explicitly\n// instead of reading an undocumented key from the edition body map.\n```",
